an)|Zero]]\n|Also in ''[[Ultimate Marvel vs. Capcom 3]]''\n|\n|-\n| {{dts|2011|03|22|format=y}} || ''[[Dissidia 012 Final Fantasy]]'' || Firion || ||<ref name=\"btva\"/>\n|-\n| {{dts|2011|06|28|format=y}} || ''[[Super Street Fighter IV: Arcade Edition]]'' || [[List of Street Fighter characters#Yun and Yang|Yang]] || ||<ref name=\"btva\"/>\n|-\n| {{dts|2011|12|20|format=y}} || ''[[Star Wars: The Old Republic]]'' || Torian Cadera || ||<ref name=\"btva\"/>\n|-\n| {{dts|2011|03|22|format=y}} || ''[[Dissidia: Final Fantasy]] || [[Firion]] || ||<ref name=\"btva\"/>\n|-\n| {{dts|2012|02|28|format=y}} || ''[[Binary Domain]]'' || Kurosawa || ||<ref name=\"btva\"/>\n|-\n| {{dts|2013|06|04|format=y}} || ''[[Marvel Heroes (video game)|Marvel Heroes]]'' || Daniel Rand / Iron Fist || ||<ref>{{cite tweet | user=johnnyyongbosch | number=661783772652703744|title=It's been announced, I'm voicing #ironfist for #marvelheroes. Excited for this one!|date=November 3, 2015|accessdate=November 4, 2015}}</ref>\n|-\n| {{dts|2013|08|27|format=y}} || ''[[Killer Is Dead]]'' || Tokio || ||<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.siliconera.com/2013/07/16/killer-is-dead-to-have-dual-audio-voice-tracks/|title=Killer is Dead To Have Dual Audio Voice Tracks|author=|date=July 16, 2013|work=siliconera.com|accessdate=October 21, 2016}}</ref><!-- btva references siliconera -->\n|-\n| {{dts|2014|09|02|format=y}} || ''[[Danganronpa 2: Goodbye Despair]]'' || Hajime Hinata / Izuru Kamukura || ||<ref>{{cite web|url=https://twitter.com/PowerJusho_KH13/status/487057154231107584|title=@johnnyyongbosch are you voicing Hajime Hinata for Danganronpa 2?I can hear your voice in it and I want to be sure. [Tweet liked by Bosch]|last=Power Jusho|date=2014-07-09|website=@PowerJusho_KH13|language=en|access-date=2019-08-04}}</ref>\n|-\n| {{dts|2014|10|07|format=y}} || ''[[Tenkai Knights: Brave Battle]]'' || Guren Nash, Bravenwolf || ||<ref name=\"btva\"/>\n|-\n| {{dts|2014|09|30|format=y}} || ''[[Persona 4 Arena Ultimax]]'' || Tohru